109
00:05:52,470 --> 00:05:53,150
He's back

110
00:05:53,300 --> 00:05:54,350
with Miss Qinghe.

111
00:05:54,350 --> 00:05:55,190
Qinghe.

112
00:05:55,430 --> 00:05:55,940
Luo,

113
00:05:57,750 --> 00:05:59,550
