155
00:08:12,490 --> 00:08:15,720
[Miao's Mansion]

156
00:08:21,740 --> 00:08:22,710
Have some tea.

157
00:08:23,710 --> 00:08:25,830
What do you want to say?

158
00:08:25,830 --> 00:08:27,670
Why are you so mysterious?

159
00:08:29,910 --> 00:08:30,630
Langyue,

160
00:08:32,190 --> 00:08:33,070
