278
00:14:21,550 --> 00:14:23,830
the way of internal affairs.

279
00:14:26,310 --> 00:14:27,390
We two countries can communicate each other

280
00:14:29,190 --> 00:14:30,140
to gain experience.

281
00:14:30,990 --> 00:14:33,110
